---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <section style="padding-top: 60px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <span class="tag sanskrit">॥ व्यवस्थायाः सत्यम् ॥</span>
            <span class="tag">Audit</span>
            <h1>Systems <span class="highlight">Audit</span></h1>
            <p class="lead" style="max-width: 650px;">
                Understand what is limiting your digital presence, knowledge, and operations before investing in solutions.
            </p>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                <span style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--accent);">Fixed Price: ₹4,999</span>
                <span style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-muted);">|</span>
                <span style="font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Timeline: 7 Business Days</span>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-dim); padding-left: 1rem;">Not every application is accepted. If I do not believe a Systems Audit will provide meaningful value, I will decline the engagement before requesting payment.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding-top: 40px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <h2>Problems Hide Behind Problems</h2>
            <ul class="structural">
                <li>A website problem may be a positioning problem.</li>
                <li>A content problem may be a knowledge problem.</li>
                <li>An operations problem may be a systems problem.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The purpose of a Systems Audit is to identify what is actually happening before deciding what to do next.</p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;">What You'll Receive</h2>
            <div class="process-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem;">
                <div style="background: var(--surface); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border);">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Systems Audit Report</h3>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">
                        <li>• Executive Summary</li>
                        <li>• Current State Assessment</li>
                        <li>• Key Findings</li>
                        <li>• Structural Weaknesses</li>
                        <li>• Bottleneck Identification</li>
                        <li>• Opportunity Analysis</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div style="background: var(--surface); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border);">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Prioritized Recommendations</h3>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">
                        <li>• Immediate Priorities</li>
                        <li>• Short-Term Improvements</li>
                        <li>• Longer-Term Opportunities</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 1rem;">Review Session</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">A live 60-minute review session to discuss findings, recommendations, and next steps.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding-top: 40px; border-bottom: none;">
        <div class="container reading" style="max-width: var(--container);">
            <h2>Request a Systems Audit</h2>
            <p>The application typically takes 5 minutes to complete.</p>

            <form data-netlify="true" method="POST" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <p class="hidden" style="display: none;">
                    <label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
                </p>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem;">
                    <div>
                        <label style="display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">Full Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text);" />
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label style="display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">Email Address</label>
                        <input type="email" name="email" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text);" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label style="display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">Phone Number</label>
                    <input type="tel" name="phone" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text);" />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label style="display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">Business Name (Optional)</label>
                    <input type="text" name="business" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text);" />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label style="display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">What is your biggest current challenge?</label>
                    <textarea name="challenge" rows="3" required style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text);"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label style="display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 0.2rem;">Areas you'd like reviewed</label>
                    <select name="areas" style="width: 100%; padding: 0.7rem; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; color: var(--text);">
                        <option value="digital-presence">Digital Presence</option>
                        <option value="knowledge-systems">Knowledge Systems</option>
                        <option value="business-operations">Business Operations</option>
                        <option value="all">All of the above</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-block">Request a Systems Audit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>